<tr>
<th rowspan="3"><a href="/wiki/Romania" title="Romania">Romania</a></th>
<td><a href="/wiki/PM_md._63" title="PM md. 63" class="mw-redirect">PM md. 63</a> (AKM), <a href="/wiki/PM_md._65" title="PM md. 65" class="mw-redirect">PM md. 65</a> (AKMS), <a href="/wiki/PM_md._63" title="PM md. 63" class="mw-redirect">PM md. 90</a> (AKMS), collectively exported under the umbrella name <a href="/wiki/AIM_(rifle)" title="AIM (rifle)">AIM or AIMS</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><a href="/wiki/PA_md._86" title="PA md. 86" class="mw-redirect">PA md. 86</a> (AK-74), exported as the <a href="/wiki/AIM_(rifle)" title="AIM (rifle)">AIMS-74</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
